<section class="section wrap">
  <div class="section-tag">Core Capabilities</div>
  <h2 class="section-h2">Built for operators who manage real complexity.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">Six core modules that cover the full lifecycle of every piece of equipment in your network — from the day it arrives to the day it leaves the floor.</p>
  <div class="feature-grid reveal">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8m-4-4v4"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card-title">Full Inventory Management</div>
      <div class="feature-card-desc">Track brand, model, condition, purchase date, and warranty for every cardio and strength piece in your network. Full edit capabilities, archiving, and multi-location organization. Always know exactly what you own and where it is.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card-title">Live Equipment Status</div>
      <div class="feature-card-desc">Know which units are running, which need attention, and which are down — across every location, in real time. Stop relying on member complaints as your early warning system. Get ahead of issues before they hit the floor.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card-title">Custom PM Scheduling</div>
      <div class="feature-card-desc">Usage-based or calendar-based maintenance notifications delivered automatically to your team. Catch problems before they become member complaints. Build a maintenance culture that prevents, not just reacts.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 000 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 001.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 01-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 01-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 017.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card-title">Service & Task Tracking</div>
      <div class="feature-card-desc">Create and assign service tasks to your team. Track complete history for every machine. Log work orders, technician visits, parts replaced, and resolution time. Keep every machine in working order with a clear paper trail.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="5 12 3 12 12 3 21 12 19 12"/><path d="M19 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H7a2 2 0 01-2-2v-7"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card-title">Equipment Transfer & Storage</div>
      <div class="feature-card-desc">Move equipment between locations or into storage. Track its complete history wherever it goes. Know the full lifecycle of every asset — from original deployment to transfer to eventual retirement — across your entire portfolio.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card-title">Analytic Reporting</div>
      <div class="feature-card-desc">Self-serve reports on usage, availability, saturation, and peak periods — updated automatically. Or request custom equipment studies from the Ecofit analytics team for deeper decisions on procurement, rotation, and club modeling.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

